Steps to run code:

$ python3 main.py
$ directory**
<displacements outputed>


**all images are present in 'images' folder within lab3. When entering directory, please end with a slash
Example: /home/fall/lab3/images/


Unaligned (color) images, SSD, and NCC images are all saved in the lab3 folder. Note that the input images are processed randomly, not in order (1-6).
__________________________________________

Libraries required: PIL, numpy, sys, os, pathlib

